cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel formulation for multiclass universum SVM and presents empirical results to demonstrate its effectiveness. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed method is evaluated on computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) datasets, indicating that these sub-categories are also likely. Finally, the use of a span bound for model selection suggests that the paper may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
